sted method of the given spider, recording extraction errors in results.\",\n    \"ContractsManager.tested_methods_from_spidercls\": \"Return the names of the methods of the given spidercls whose docstrings contain contract annotations.\",\n    \"_create_testcase.ContractTestCase\": \"Synthetic TestCase subclass whose string form names the spider, method and contract hook being exercised.\"\n  }\n}\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":11302,"cache_read_input_tokens":66537,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":11302},"output_tokens":4,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"455c3339-708e-46be-b783-7b0d8d3ce5a3","uuid":"4e899825-fe2e-4284-98d2-286012917220","request_id":"req_011CbyPVLKPyxouNQQqki7Rs"}
